urls.title: The Pangburn Hangout
urls.description: This is where the Pangburn Community hangs out. Travis Pangburn is a Philosopher, Artist and Producer that is best known for producing some of the largest-scale intellectual discussions in history. Most notably, the Sam Harris vs Jordan Peterson series. This discussion Community was born out of this work. We discuss philosophy, art, science & life. The show hosts are seasoned Pangburn veterans that bring their own conversational flavor to the table. All ideas are welcome. Let art & science inspire.
